TITLE:BAX Documentation - Complete Guide
DESC:Complete documentation for BAX static site generator - installation, configuration, content creation, and deployment.
IMG:https://placehold.co/1200x400/0f172a/ffffff?text=BAX+Docs

H1:BAX Documentation

H2:Table of Contents
UL:
LI:<a href="#intro">Introduction</a>
LI:<a href="#install">Installation</a>
LI:<a href="#config">Configuration</a>
